// ── Section G — N1 vs RNS hardware delta (verify_paper_p002 anchors) ──

@F BRAINWIRE-AR-N1-VS-RNS-CHANNEL = N1 1024 ch / RNS 4 ch = 256× ratio; N1 20 kHz / RNS 250 Hz = 80× sample rate :: hardware_comparison [10]
